data.description: An in-town home with that north woods feeling. Inside the house is knotty pine and beamed ceilings on the main level with 2 bedrooms and a bathroom. Lots of counter space in the kitchen with a breakfast nook as well as a counter top eating area. Downstairs is another bedroom with egress window, a cozy family room, a hobby room and bathroom with a sauna! Shared driveway with a large 2 stall garage with a lean-to for extra storage, a cement patio, garden and a nice spacious back yard. This house is a must see!
